STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Alton BRYANT, a/k/a Rashad McKnight, Alquan Muslim, Dick Dick, Quan, Patrick Bryant and Dwayne Brown, Defendant-Petitioner. C-340 September Term 2018
081223 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 16, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004169-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
